       IDENTIFICATION DIVISION.
       PROGRAM-ID.    ARI80204.
      ******************************************************************
      *     PROGRAMA ARI80204.                                         *
      *                                                                *
      *     Utilizadores
      ******************************************************************
      *     LOG ALTERACOES:                                            *
      *   USER     / DATA     /   REFERENCIA / OBSERVACOES             *
      *                                                                *
      *                                                                *
      ******************************************************************
       ENVIRONMENT DIVISION.
       CONFIGURATION SECTION.
       DATA DIVISION.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       WORKING-STORAGE SECTION.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       01  FILLER                          PIC X(40) VALUE
           'INICIO WORKING-STORAGE ARI80204         '.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            DECLARACOES DE DB2
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
           EXEC SQL INCLUDE ARCD0103 END-EXEC.
           EXEC SQL INCLUDE ARCD0200 END-EXEC.
           EXEC SQL INCLUDE ARCD3000 END-EXEC.
           EXEC SQL INCLUDE ARCD2000 END-EXEC.
           EXEC SQL INCLUDE SQLCA    END-EXEC.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       01 WS-SQL-AUXILIARY.
         05 IND-NULL                       PIC S9(04) BINARY.

      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            MENSAGEM DE INPUT E  OUTPUT
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       COPY ARCV8020.
       COPY ARCV8021.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            AREAS DE TRABALHO
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       COPY VIAL0010.
       COPY VIAW0005.
       COPY VIAK0001.
       COPY VIAK0002.
       COPY ARCK0001.
       COPY ARCK0002.
       COPY VIAL0015.
      *
       COPY ARCL2505.
       COPY ETCL0002.
      *
CDT    COPY TGCL1000.
CDT    COPY TGCL2000.
CDT    COPY TGCK0002.
      *
       COPY VIAL1030.
       COPY AQCW0009.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            CONSTANTES
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       01  WS-CONSTANTES.
           05 CON-ARVT0103           PIC X(08) VALUE 'ARVT0103'.
           05 CON-ARVT0200           PIC X(08) VALUE 'ARVT0200'.
           05 CON-ARVT3000           PIC X(08) VALUE 'ARVT3000'.
           05 CON-ARVT2000           PIC X(08) VALUE 'ARVT2000'.
           05 WS-PROGNAME            PIC X(08) VALUE 'ARI80204'.
CDT        05 CON-CTABELA-CLINGUA    PIC X(05) VALUE 'AR001'.
CDT        05 CON-CTABELA-ISTATUS    PIC X(05) VALUE 'AR007'.
           05 CON-CTABELA-CTIPOUTIL  PIC X(05) VALUE 'AR066'.
           05 CON-DATAMAXIMA         PIC X(10) VALUE '9999-12-31'.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            VARIAVEIS
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       01  WS-VARIAVEIS.
           05 AUX-CPERFIL                  PIC X(12).
           05 WS-CPERFIL                   PIC X(12).
CDT        05 WS-CTABELA                   PIC X(05) VALUE SPACES.
CDT        05 WS-CCOD                      PIC X(40) VALUE SPACES.
           05 WS-EMAIL                     PIC X(50) VALUE SPACES.
           05 WS-NOTE                      PIC X(500) VALUE SPACES.
           05 WS-ASSUNTO                   PIC X(050) VALUE SPACES.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       01  FILLER                        PIC X(40) VALUE
           'FIM DA WORKING-STORAGE ARI80204         '.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       LINKAGE SECTION.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       COPY VIAL0004.
      *
            EXEC SQL INCLUDE VIAP0009 END-EXEC.
      *
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            0000-MAINLINE
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       0000-MAINLINE.
      *
           PERFORM 1000-INICIO-PROGRAMA
              THRU 1099-INICIO-PROGRAMA-EXIT.

           PERFORM 2000-PROC-PROGRAMA
              THRU 2099-PROC-PROGRAMA-EXIT.

           PERFORM 3000-FINAL-PROGRAMA
              THRU 3099-FINAL-PROGRAMA-EXIT.
      *
       0099-MAINLINE-EXIT.
           COPY VIAP0004.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            1000-INICIO-PROGRAMA
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       1000-INICIO-PROGRAMA.
      *
           IF VIAL0001-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '1000-INICIO-PROGRAMA' TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              MOVE 'ARCV8020-NOTP       ' TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-NM(1)
              MOVE  ARCV8020-NOTP         TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-VLR(1)
              PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.

           MOVE VIAL0001-MENSAGEM-INPUT    TO ARCV8020-MSG.
           MOVE ARCV8020-ASE               TO ARCV8021-ASE.
      *
       1099-INICIO-PROGRAMA-EXIT.
           EXIT.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            2000-PROC-PROGRAMA
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       2000-PROC-PROGRAMA.

           MOVE ARCV8020-ADE               TO ARCV8021-ADE.

           PERFORM 2100-VALIDACOES
              THRU 2199-VALIDACOES-EXIT
      *
           IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
              PERFORM 2200-INSERE-DADOS
                 THRU 2299-INSERE-DADOS-EXIT
           END-IF.
      *
           IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
              PERFORM 2300-ENVIA-EMAIL
                 THRU 2300-ENVIA-EMAIL-EXIT
           END-IF.

       2099-PROC-PROGRAMA-EXIT.
           EXIT.

      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *                   2100-VALIDACOES
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       2100-VALIDACOES.

           IF VIAL0001-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '2100-VALIDACOES     ' TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.

      * Valida se o perfil introduzido é master, se for dá erro
           PERFORM 2110-VALIDA-PERFILMASTER
              THRU 2110-VALIDA-PERFILMASTER-EXIT.

      *------------------------------------------------------------*
      *   Valida se o perfil introduzido tem o msm master do       *
      *   perfil do utilizador logado no site correspondente       *
      *   assim os da aplicaçăo da Via só acedem aos perfis da Via *
      *   e os utilizadores das outras aplicaçőes também só acedem *
      *   aos perfis dessas aplicaçőes                             *
      *------------------------------------------------------------*

      * Obtem master do perfil do utilizador logado
           IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
              PERFORM 2120-OBT-MASTER-USER
                 THRU 2120-OBT-MASTER-USER-EXIT
           END-IF.

      * Obtem master do perfil introduzido de input
           IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
              MOVE ARCV8020-CPERFIL TO WS-CPERFIL
              PERFORM 2130-OBT-MASTER-PERFIL
                 THRU 2130-OBT-MASTER-PERFIL-EXIT
           END-IF.

      * Valida o email
           IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
              PERFORM 2150-VALIDA-EMAIL
                 THRU 2150-VALIDA-EMAIL-EXIT
           END-IF.

              MOVE '2100-VALIDACOES     ' TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              MOVE 'AUX-CPERFIL         ' TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-NM(1)
              MOVE  AUX-CPERFIL           TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-VLR(1)
              MOVE 'ARCL2505-CPERFILMAST' TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-NM(2)
              MOVE  ARCL2505-CPERFILMAST  TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-VLR(2)
              PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           .
      *Valida se ambos os perfis tęm o mesmo master
      *Compara se aux-perfil (master do user logado) é igual
      *ao ARCL2505-CPERFILMAST que é o master do perfil de input
      *- SE ARCL2505-CPERFILMAST E DO TIPO 'C' - CLIENTE
      *  validamos se ja tem algum user associado. Se tiver n cria
      *    IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
      *       IF AUX-CPERFIL NOT EQUAL ARCL2505-CPERFILMAST
      *          IF ARCL2505-INDPERM-MASTER EQUAL 'C'
      *             PERFORM 2140-VALIDA-USER
      *                THRU 2140-VALIDA-USER-EXIT
      *          END-IF
      *
      *          IF (ARCL2505-INDPERM-MASTER EQUAL 'C' AND
      *              DB2-OK)
      *          OR ARCL2505-INDPERM-MASTER NOT EQUAL 'C'
      *             MOVE VIAK0002-ERROS-FUNCAO
      *               TO VIAL0002-IND-ERROS
      *             MOVE ARCK0002-STATUS-ACTIVO
      *               TO ARCV8021-CPERFIL-S
      *             MOVE ARCK0001-PERFIL-INVA
      *               TO ARCV8021-CPERFIL-MSG
      *          END-IF
      *       END-IF
      *    END-IF.

       2199-VALIDACOES-EXIT.
           EXIT.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *                   2110-VALIDA-PERFILMASTER
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       2110-VALIDA-PERFILMASTER.

           IF VIAL0001-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '2110-VALIDA-PERFILMASTER' TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.

           MOVE ARCV8020-CPERFIL     TO ARCD2000-CPERFIL

           EXEC SQL
             SELECT   CPERFIL
                    , INDPERM
                    , CPERFILM
               INTO  :ARCD2000-CPERFIL
                    ,:ARCD2000-INDPERM
                    ,:ARCD2000-CPERFILM
               FROM ARVT2002_INFPERFIL
              WHERE CPERFIL = :ARCD2000-CPERFIL
           END-EXEC

           MOVE CON-ARVT2000         TO VIAL0002-TABLE-NAME.

           PERFORM 9020-DB2CHECK
              THRU 9029-DB2CHECK-EXIT.

           IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
              IF NOT DB2-OK
                 MOVE VIAK0002-ERROS-FUNCAO
                   TO VIAL0002-IND-ERROS
                 MOVE ARCK0002-STATUS-ACTIVO
                   TO ARCV8021-CPERFIL-S
                 MOVE ARCK0001-ERR-CPERFIL
                   TO ARCV8021-CPERFIL-MSG
              END-IF

              IF DB2-OK AND
                 ARCD2000-INDPERM NOT EQUAL ARCK0002-N-PERFIL-MASTER
                 MOVE VIAK0002-ERROS-FUNCAO
                   TO VIAL0002-IND-ERROS
                 MOVE ARCK0002-STATUS-ACTIVO
                   TO ARCV8021-CPERFIL-S
                 MOVE ARCK0001-ESTE-PER-AESTEUSER-N
                   TO ARCV8021-CPERFIL-MSG
                 ELSE
                    CONTINUE
              END-IF
           END-IF.

       2110-VALIDA-PERFILMASTER-EXIT.
           EXIT.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *                   2120-OBT-MASTER-USER
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       2120-OBT-MASTER-USER.

           IF VIAL0001-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '2120-OBT-MASTER-USER'  TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.

           INITIALIZE ARCL2505-COMMAREA REPLACING NUMERIC BY ZEROES
                                             ALPHANUMERIC BY SPACES.

           MOVE VIAL0001-CUTILIZA-I        TO ARCL2505-CUSERID.

           CALL ARCL2505-ROTINA USING ETCL0002-COMMAREA
                                      ARCL2505-COMMAREA.

           IF VIAL0001-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE 'OBTEM MASTER        '  TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              MOVE 'ARCL2505-CPERFILMAST'  TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-NM(1)
              MOVE  ARCL2505-CPERFILMAST   TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-VLR(1)
              PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.

           IF ETCL0002-SEM-ERROS
              IF DB2-OK
                 MOVE ARCL2505-CPERFILMAST TO AUX-CPERFIL
              ELSE
                 MOVE ETCL0002-IND-ERROS
                   TO VIAL0002-IND-ERROS
                 MOVE ARCK0002-STATUS-ACTIVO
                   TO ARCV8021-CPERFIL-S
                 MOVE ETCL0002-ST-ERRO
                   TO ARCV8021-CPERFIL-MSG
           END-IF.

       2120-OBT-MASTER-USER-EXIT.
           EXIT.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *                   2130-OBT-MASTER-PERFIL.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       2130-OBT-MASTER-PERFIL.

           IF VIAL0001-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '2130-OBT-MASTER-PERFIL-USER' TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.

           INITIALIZE ARCL2505-COMMAREA REPLACING NUMERIC BY ZEROES
                                             ALPHANUMERIC BY SPACES.

           MOVE ARCV8020-CPERFIL           TO ARCL2505-CPERFIL.

           CALL ARCL2505-ROTINA USING ETCL0002-COMMAREA
                                      ARCL2505-COMMAREA.

           MOVE '2130-OBT-MASTER-PERFIL-USER' TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
           MOVE 'ARCL2505-CPERFIL           ' TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-NM(1)
           MOVE  ARCL2505-CPERFIL             TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-VLR(1)
           MOVE 'ARCL2505-INDPERM-MASTER    ' TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-NM(2)
           MOVE  ARCL2505-INDPERM-MASTER      TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-VLR(2)
           PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
              THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT

           IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
              IF NOT DB2-OK
                 MOVE ETCL0002-IND-ERROS
                   TO VIAL0002-IND-ERROS
                 MOVE ARCK0002-STATUS-ACTIVO
                   TO ARCV8021-CPERFIL-S
                 MOVE ETCL0002-ST-ERRO
                   TO ARCV8021-CPERFIL-MSG
              END-IF
           END-IF.

       2130-OBT-MASTER-PERFIL-EXIT.
           EXIT.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *                   2140-VALIDA-USER
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       2140-VALIDA-USER.

           IF VIAL0001-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '2140-VALIDA-USER'         TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              MOVE 'ARCV8020-CPERFIL     '    TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-NM(1)
              MOVE  ARCV8020-CPERFIL          TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-VLR(1)
              MOVE 'ARCL2505-INDPERM-MASTER ' TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-NM(2)
              MOVE  ARCL2505-INDPERM-MASTER   TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-VLR(2)
              PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.

           MOVE ARCV8020-CPERFIL           TO ARCD0103-CPERFIL.

           EXEC SQL
             SELECT CPERFIL
               INTO :ARCD0103-CPERFIL
               FROM ARVT0103
              WHERE UPPER(CPERFIL) = UPPER(:ARCD0103-CPERFIL)
              FETCH FIRST ROW ONLY
           END-EXEC.

           MOVE CON-ARVT0103               TO VIAL0002-TABLE-NAME

           PERFORM 9020-DB2CHECK
              THRU 9029-DB2CHECK-EXIT

           IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
              IF NOT DB2-OK AND NOT DB2-NOTFND
                 MOVE ETCL0002-IND-ERROS
                   TO VIAL0002-IND-ERROS
                 MOVE ARCK0002-STATUS-ACTIVO
                   TO ARCV8021-CPERFIL-S
                 MOVE ETCL0002-ST-ERRO
                   TO ARCV8021-CPERFIL-MSG
              END-IF
           END-IF.

       2140-VALIDA-USER-EXIT.
           EXIT.

      *-------------------------------------------------------------*
      *                   2150-VALIDA-EMAIL                         *
      *-------------------------------------------------------------*
       2150-VALIDA-EMAIL.

           IF VIAL0001-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '2150-VALIDA-EMAIL      ' TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.

           INITIALIZE VIAL1030-COMMAREA.

           MOVE ARCV8020-GEMAIL              TO VIAL1030-EMAIL.

           CALL VIAL1030-NM-ROTINA USING VIAL1030-COMMAREA
                                         ETCL0002-COMMAREA.

           IF NOT ETCL0002-SEM-ERROS
              MOVE ETCL0002-IND-ERROS
                TO VIAL0002-IND-ERROS
              MOVE ARCK0002-STATUS-ACTIVO
                TO ARCV8021-GEMAIL-S
              MOVE ETCL0002-NR-ERRO
                TO ARCV8021-GEMAIL-MSG
              MOVE ETCL0002-CAPLIC-ERRO
                TO ARCV8021-GEMAIL-CAPLIC
           END-IF.

       2150-VALIDA-EMAIL-EXIT.
           EXIT.

      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *                   2200-INSERE-DADOS
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       2200-INSERE-DADOS.

           IF VIAL0001-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '2200-INSERE-DADOS      ' TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.

           MOVE ARCV8020-GUSERNAME         TO ARCD0103-GUSERNAME
                                              ARCD3000-GUSERNAME.
           MOVE ARCV8020-CNOME             TO ARCD0103-CNOME.
           MOVE ARCV8020-CFUNCAO           TO ARCD0103-CFUNCAO.
           MOVE ARCV8020-CTIPOUTIL         TO ARCD0103-CTIPOUTIL.
           MOVE ARCV8020-CPERFIL           TO ARCD0103-CPERFIL
                                              ARCD3000-CPERFIL.
           MOVE ARCV8020-CLINGUA           TO ARCD0103-CLINGUA.
           MOVE ARCV8020-GPASSWORD         TO ARCD0103-GPASSWORD.
           MOVE ARCV8020-CEMPRESA          TO ARCD0103-CEMPRESA.
           MOVE ARCV8020-GEMAIL            TO ARCD0103-GEMAIL.
           MOVE ARCK0002-PENDENT-STATUS    TO ARCD0103-ISTATUS.
           MOVE ARCV8020-DDATINI           TO ARCD0103-DDATINI.
           MOVE CON-DATAMAXIMA             TO ARCD0103-DDATFIM.

      * Campos presentes na tabela, mas fora da transacçăo
      *>>>
           MOVE ZEROES                     TO ARCD0103-CCENTRO.
           MOVE ZEROES                     TO ARCD0103-CMOED.
           MOVE ZEROES                     TO ARCD0103-MCUSTMED.
      *<<<

           MOVE VIAL0001-CUTILIZA-I        TO ARCD0103-CUSERID
                                              ARCD3000-CUSERID.

           IF VIAL0001-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE ARCD0103-GUSERNAME    TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-NM(1)
              MOVE ARCD0103-CNOME        TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-VLR(1)
              MOVE ARCD0103-CFUNCAO      TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-NM(2)
              MOVE ARCD0103-CTIPOUTIL    TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-NM(2)
              MOVE ARCD0103-CPERFIL      TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-VLR(2)
              MOVE ARCD0103-CLINGUA      TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-NM(3)
              MOVE ARCD0103-CEMPRESA     TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-VLR(4)
              MOVE ARCD0103-GEMAIL       TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-VLR(4)
              MOVE ARCD0103-ISTATUS      TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-NM(4)
              MOVE ARCD0103-CCENTRO      TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-NM(5)
              MOVE ARCD0103-CMOED        TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-VLR(5)
      **      MOVE ARCD0103-MCUSTMED     TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-NM(6)
              MOVE ARCD0103-DDATINI      TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-VLR(6)
              MOVE ARCD0103-DDATFIM      TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-NM(7)
              MOVE ARCV8021-NOTP         TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-NM(8)
              PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.

           EXEC SQL
                 INSERT INTO
                ARVT0103
                (
                   GUSERNAME
                 , CNOME
                 , CFUNCAO
                 , CPERFIL
                 , CLINGUA
                 , GPASSWORD
                 , ISTATUS
                 , CEMPRESA
                 , CCENTRO
                 , CMOED
                 , MCUSTMED
                 , DDATINI
                 , DDATFIM
                 , CUSERID
                 , HTIMEST
                 , GEMAIL
                 , CTIPOUTIL
                )
                VALUES (
                       :ARCD0103-GUSERNAME
                     , :ARCD0103-CNOME
                     , :ARCD0103-CFUNCAO
                     , :ARCD0103-CPERFIL
                     , :ARCD0103-CLINGUA
                     , :ARCD0103-GPASSWORD
                     , :ARCD0103-ISTATUS
                     , :ARCD0103-CEMPRESA
                     , :ARCD0103-CCENTRO
                     , :ARCD0103-CMOED
                     , :ARCD0103-MCUSTMED
                     , CURRENT_DATE
                     , :ARCD0103-DDATFIM
                     , :ARCD0103-CUSERID
                     , CURRENT TIMESTAMP
                     , :ARCD0103-GEMAIL
                     , :ARCD0103-CTIPOUTIL
                )
           END-EXEC

           MOVE CON-ARVT0103               TO VIAL0002-TABLE-NAME

           PERFORM 9020-DB2CHECK
              THRU 9029-DB2CHECK-EXIT

           IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
              IF DB2-OK
                 MOVE ARCD0103-ISTATUS TO ARCV8021-ISTATUS
              END-IF
              IF DB2-DUPREC
                 MOVE VIAK0002-ERROS-FUNCAO
                      TO VIAL0002-IND-ERROS
                 MOVE ARCK0002-STATUS-ACTIVO
                        TO ARCV8021-GUSERNAME-S
                 MOVE ARCK0001-GUSERNAME-A-EXISTS
                        TO ARCV8021-GUSERNAME-MSG
              ELSE
                 IF NOT DB2-OK
                    MOVE VIAK0002-ABEND-DB2
                         TO VIAL0002-IND-ERROS
                    MOVE VIAK0001-ERRO-DB2
                         TO VIAL0002-COD-ERRO-GRAVE
                 END-IF
              END-IF
           END-IF

           EXEC SQL
                   INSERT INTO
                  ARVT3000_PERFISUSER
                  (
                     GUSERNAME
                   , CPERFIL
                   , CUSERID
                   , HTIMEST
                   )
              VALUES (
                     :ARCD3000-GUSERNAME
                   , :ARCD3000-CPERFIL
                   , :ARCD3000-CUSERID
                   , CURRENT TIMESTAMP
                   )
           END-EXEC

           MOVE CON-ARVT3000               TO VIAL0002-TABLE-NAME

           PERFORM 9020-DB2CHECK
              THRU 9029-DB2CHECK-EXIT

           IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
              IF DB2-DUPREC
                 MOVE VIAK0002-ERROS-FUNCAO
                      TO VIAL0002-IND-ERROS
                 MOVE ARCK0002-STATUS-ACTIVO
                      TO ARCV8021-GUSERNAME-S
                 MOVE ARCK0001-GUSERNAME-A-EXISTS
                      TO ARCV8021-GUSERNAME-MSG
                 MOVE ARCK0002-STATUS-ACTIVO
                      TO ARCV8021-CPERFIL-S
                 MOVE ARCK0001-CPERFIL-A-EXISTS
                      TO ARCV8021-CPERFIL-MSG
              ELSE
                 IF NOT DB2-OK
                    MOVE VIAK0002-ABEND-DB2
                         TO VIAL0002-IND-ERROS
                    MOVE VIAK0001-ERRO-DB2
                         TO VIAL0002-COD-ERRO-GRAVE
                 END-IF
              END-IF
           END-IF.

       2299-INSERE-DADOS-EXIT.
           EXIT.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *                   2300-ENVIA-EMAIL
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       2300-ENVIA-EMAIL.
      *
           IF VIAL0001-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '2330-ENVIA-EMAIL     ' TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.
      *
           MOVE VIAL1030-EMAIL             TO WS-EMAIL
      *
           STRING 'Foi criado o novo utilizador '  DELIMITED BY SIZE
                  ARCV8020-GUSERNAME               DELIMITED BY ' '
                  ' de acesso ao portal Backoffice '
                                                   DELIMITED BY SIZE
                  ' com a senha provisória '       DELIMITED BY SIZE
                  ARCV8020-NOTP                    DELIMITED BY SIZE
                  '. No 1ş acesso vai ser pedida ' DELIMITED BY SIZE
                  ' alteraçăo da mesma.'           DELIMITED BY SIZE
           INTO WS-NOTE
      *
           MOVE 'Password de acesso ao portal Backoffice'
                                           TO WS-ASSUNTO
      *
           CALL 'ARL00P00C' USING AQCW0009-DATA
                                  WS-EMAIL
                                  WS-ASSUNTO
                                  WS-NOTE.
      *
       2300-ENVIA-EMAIL-EXIT.
           EXIT.

      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            3000-FINAL-PROGRAMA
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       3000-FINAL-PROGRAMA.

           IF VIAL0001-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '3000-FINAL-PROGRAMA     ' TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.

CDT   *    IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
      *       PERFORM 3100-VAL-CAMPOS
      *          THRU 3100-VAL-CAMPOS-EXIT
CDT   *    END-IF.

           MOVE ARCV8021-MSG               TO VIAL0001-MENSAGEM-OUTPUT.
           MOVE ARCV8021-LENGTH            TO VIAL0001-LENGTH-MSG.
           MOVE ARCV8021-NR-CAMPOS         TO VIAL0001-NR-CAMPOS.
           MOVE ZEROES
             TO VIAL0001-OCORRENCIAS.

       3099-FINAL-PROGRAMA-EXIT.
           EXIT.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *                   3100-VAL-CAMPOS
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       3100-VAL-CAMPOS.
      *
           IF VIAL0001-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '3100-VAL-CAMPOS' TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.


           IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS AND ARCV8020-CLINGUA NOT EQUAL SPACES
              MOVE CON-CTABELA-CLINGUA         TO WS-CTABELA
              MOVE ARCV8020-CLINGUA            TO WS-CCOD
              PERFORM 3200-VAL-TAB-ART05
                 THRU 3200-VAL-TAB-ART05-EXIT
              IF NOT VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
                 MOVE TGCL2000-CCOD-S       TO ARCV8021-CLINGUA-S
                 MOVE TGCL2000-CCOD-CAPLIC  TO ARCV8021-CLINGUA-CAPLIC
                 MOVE TGCL2000-CCOD-MSG     TO ARCV8021-CLINGUA-MSG
                 MOVE TGCL2000-GDESC        TO ARCV8021-XDESCCLINGUA
              ELSE
                 MOVE TGCL2000-GDESC        TO ARCV8020-XDESCCLINGUA
              END-IF
           END-IF.
      *
           IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS AND ARCV8020-ISTATUS NOT EQUAL SPACES
              MOVE CON-CTABELA-ISTATUS         TO WS-CTABELA
              MOVE ARCV8020-ISTATUS            TO WS-CCOD
              PERFORM 3200-VAL-TAB-ART05
                 THRU 3200-VAL-TAB-ART05-EXIT
              IF NOT VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
                 MOVE TGCL2000-CCOD-S       TO ARCV8021-ISTATUS-S
                 MOVE TGCL2000-CCOD-CAPLIC  TO ARCV8021-ISTATUS-CAPLIC
                 MOVE TGCL2000-CCOD-MSG     TO ARCV8021-ISTATUS-MSG
                 MOVE TGCL2000-GDESC        TO ARCV8021-XDESCISTATUS
              ELSE
                 MOVE TGCL2000-GDESC        TO ARCV8020-XDESCISTATUS
              END-IF
           END-IF.
      *

       3100-VAL-CAMPOS-EXIT.
           EXIT.

      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *                   3200-VAL-TAB-ART05
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       3200-VAL-TAB-ART05.
      *
           MOVE '3200-VAL-TAB-ART05' TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID

      *
           INITIALIZE TGCL2000-MSG       REPLACING  NUMERIC BY ZEROES
                                               ALPHANUMERIC BY SPACES.

           MOVE WS-CTABELA                TO TGCL2000-CTABELA
           MOVE WS-CCOD                   TO TGCL2000-CCOD

           PERFORM CALL-TGCP2000
              THRU CALL-TGCP2000-EXIT.

       3200-VAL-TAB-ART05-EXIT.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
           EXEC SQL INCLUDE VIAP0003 END-EXEC.
      *==============================================================
           COPY VIAP0010.
           COPY VIAP0016.
CDT        COPY TGCP1000.
CDT        COPY TGCP2000.
